<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Changed Successfully</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e 0%, #16a34a 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .success-notice {
            background-color: #dcfce7;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #22c55e;
        }
        
        .success-notice p {
            color: #15803d;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .security-info {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
        }
        
        .security-info p {
            color: #92400e;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .timestamp-info {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        
        .timestamp-info p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        
        .security-tips {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
        }
        
        .security-tips h3 {
            color: #1e40af;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .security-tips p {
            color: #1e40af;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .greeting {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
            
            .cta-button {
                padding: 14px 28px;
                font-size: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>âœ… Password Changed</h1>
            <p>Your password has been successfully updated</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello{{#if recipientName}} {{recipientName}}{{/if}},
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                Great news! Your password for your {{companyName}} account has been successfully changed. Your account is now secured with your new password and you can continue using the platform as normal.
            </div>
            
            <div class="success-notice">
                <p><strong>âœ… Password Update Successful:</strong> Your new password is now active and ready to use.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-info">
                <p><strong>Security Details:</strong> This change was made {{#if ipAddress}}from IP address: {{ipAddress}}{{else}}from an unknown location{{/if}} on {{changeDateTime}}.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                If you did not make this change, please contact our support team immediately as your account may have been compromised.
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="cta-button">Continue to Dashboard</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timestamp-info">
                <p><strong>Change Details:</strong></p>
                <p>Date & Time: {{changeDateTime}}</p>
                <p>IP Address: {{#if ipAddress}}{{ipAddress}}{{else}}Not available{{/if}}</p>
                <p>User Agent: {{#if userAgent}}{{userAgent}}{{else}}Not available{{/if}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-tips">
                <h3>ðŸ”’ Keep Your Account Secure</h3>
                <p><strong>Remember these security best practices:</strong></p>
                <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px; color: #1e40af;">
                    <li>Never share your password with anyone</li>
                    <li>Use a unique password for this account</li>
                    <li>Consider enabling two-factor authentication</li>
                    <li>Log out from shared or public computers</li>
                    <li>Monitor your account for any suspicious activity</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <strong>Didn't make this change?</strong><br>
                If you did not authorize this password change, please contact our security team immediately. We take account security very seriously and will help you secure your account right away.
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <strong>Next Steps:</strong>
                <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>You can now log in using your new password</li>
                    <li>All existing sessions remain active unless you choose to log out</li>
                    <li>Your account settings and data remain unchanged</li>
                    <li>Consider reviewing your security settings in your profile</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>{{companyName}} Security Team</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">
                This is an automated security notification. Please do not reply to this email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 